Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 完全迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天到最后 樱小姐也没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱小姐到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然之前也有一直没回来的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全校学生罢课抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早天枷美夏的退学令正式发表了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事会似乎想来个速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:03:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天校方决定对附中二年一班的天枷美夏作出退学处分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找替罪羊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教务办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要对理事会的决定提出抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广播后 所有对美夏退学处分定不满的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起拥到了教务办公室门口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果交涉破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍对教师的行为感到不满的学生们不愿回到教室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉锯战的罢课运动于是在校内升温
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直延续到现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我说 教导主任对学生会下达了镇压学生的命令哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会吗 那音姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然当场否决
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家都很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一班已经占领美术室 用雕塑作路障封锁中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打持久战了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以打响第一枪哦 樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 那就好好帮他们打回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学 义之君也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱内 你在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在主角也出现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是说曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你说啊 樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是大家为美夏所做的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何一个人希望美夏离开学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:05:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为美夏做这么多 我真的是非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这么做之后会有麻烦是大家不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管大家做什么 美夏的退学处分是不可能被取消的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗 杉並
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方只是受欲望支配的丑陋的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们最多不过是给扣上不良分子的帽子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以美夏不希望为了这样无谓的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁了大家的大好前途
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么才能让大家停下来 樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把你的想法告诉大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管用什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 大家一定会回应的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏的想法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈佳 广播器材的使用方法你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？嗯 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉並 广播室的钥匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我就想到会有这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试音试音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…咳…今天运势很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 这也不用说吗 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风见学园的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家安静地听我说 我是二年的天枷美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是天枷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如大家所见 现在校园内发生了大动乱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为美夏所做的事 美夏真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很遗憾 理事会的决定 美夏已经接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个决定不能收回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让天枷退学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}天枷天枷天枷…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你去广播室的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事继续下去 不但给周围的人造成困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会给大家自身带来麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏 美夏不希望大家为了美夏背上任何处分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏能转入大家所在的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起享受校园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就剩最后三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家再让我渡过三天充实的校园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 美夏就可以毫无遗憾地离开风见学园了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差几天了 就一点时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家给我一个享受平常校园生活的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 拜托了 拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天 天枷的心意确确实实地传到了大家的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀哈 杏学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 来了啊 就等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把由梦也带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学这么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她现在这么开心 好像昨天什么也没发生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 这样下去真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之也是 对天枷同学的事好像也放手不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为天枷同学希望保持那种平常的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是小恋想做些什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然 因为是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但义之的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是因为讨厌那样才和义之君分手的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽没错 真是的 奈奈佳坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 但如果真是这么想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就该小恋对自己诚实一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷把自己心里的想法告诉了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就轮到小恋站在朋友的立场去考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么去帮助天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有怎么面对义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来其实就是这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了 樱内 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利马奥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了 义之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 事前也没联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是理事会临时安排我出差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这只是理事会为了处分天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使出的调虎离山之计罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中的还轻松快活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经下了决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那义之呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之怎么看这事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么了结了真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 说实话我也在犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想为她做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷自己并不想让我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她比起自己 更关心我、由梦和班长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有风见学园的所有学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也想尊重天枷如此认真的考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让天枷就这样继续享受理所应当的最后一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像什么都没发生过一样继续过学校生活的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在这么想…很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 是不是对她太冷淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是非常好的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照义之所想的去做 这也都是为了天枷同学好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下一点时间 就一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不出什么意外就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的愿望都连成一线
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 约定好的三天期限转眼就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 结束了 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗 和美夏初次相遇时的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘都忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拳头我现在还痛着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别 别提那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我也觉得抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后也一直给樱内添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这么郑重地道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想道个谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着风见学园的学生身份还没失效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心我 我不是在感伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 要是没有你 现在美夏还不知道怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在说些有的没的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏也通过认识你 第一次发现人类不全是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由梦和朝仓学姐 杏学姐 花咲同学 月岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:16:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带板桥和杉並 和大家都成了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后也和泽井解开了心结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 樱内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏真的是机器人与人类之间的桥梁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏的愿望实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 是义之吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了这么急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 天枷同学也在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那带上天枷同学一起来体育馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体育馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋这家伙 为什么要在体育馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业生入场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在校生起立
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了 天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个是 天枷的毕业典礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏的毕业典礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 天枷同学 大家都等着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么时候策划的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞成这样不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 学生会也全力协助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳乃校长也同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是多亏小恋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这三天里月岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能让天枷同学毕业典礼可以成功举办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东奔西走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能为你做些什么真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我现在可以做到的全部了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,授予毕业证书
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业证书 天枷美夏同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在任何时候都能保持健康明朗的心态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与同学相处融洽并完成了本学园所有规定课程
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特此证明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风见学园校长芳乃樱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}舞台的后台集合 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台的后台？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 义之快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 好戏现在才登场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 饱含爽朗和激情叫出我们对美夏的爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之 这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
